hey_janaflowchart TD
    A[Subscription to  <b>/audio_and_device_info</b>:<br>512 samples<br> Chunks of 0.032s] --> B[Buffering]
    B --> C[VAD check]
    C -- speech=True --> D[Accumulate chunk window]
    D --> E[Trigger transcription]
    E --> F[ASR model faster_whisper / local]
    F --> G[Postprocess & result]
    G --> H[ /speech_result SpeechResult]

    C -- speech=False --> I[Drop or wait]

    style A fill:#FFA500
    style H fill:#FFA500

%% Notes
%% - ASR buffers audio to form a context window before sending to model.
%% - VAD can trigger or gate transcription to reduce compute.
